snippet.title: DOOMSDAY METEOR | Can Earth Stop a Planet-Ending Impact? | Full Movie
snippet.description:
A massive object is on a direct course for Earth.
Saving the planet means risking everything beyond the atmosphere.

When scientists discover a colossal meteor heading straight for Earth, they realize time is dangerously short. Early attempts to alter its path fail, forcing an international team to take a desperate risk: landing directly on the object itself. As unexpected challenges arise in space, the mission becomes a race not just against time, but against the limits of human survival.

Director: Noah Luke
Cast: Patrick Labyorteaux, Caroline Williams, Joseph Michael Harris, Anthony Jensen.
